(46, 'DEGREE PULLOVER LIGHT GREY', 'degree-pullover-light-grey', 11, 1, 50, 24, 50, '{\"S\":9,\"XL\":\"10\",\"2XL\":\"5\"}', 'h9-31532578355.jpg', '[\"h9-21532578355.jpg\",\"h9-11532578355.jpg\",\"h9-51532578355.jpg\",\"h9-61532578355.jpg\",\"h9-41532578355.jpg\"]', 'Fully fleeced with your comfort in mind, the Gymshark Degree Pullover delivers where your average pullover doesn’t.', '<p>Fully fleeced with your comfort in mind, the Gymshark Degree Pullover delivers where your average pullover doesn&rsquo;t. Providing exceptional comfort like no other, it&rsquo;s your must-have winter companion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super soft, lightweight and warm, the Degree Pullover offers protection from the cold front. With an exaggerated crossover neck, 3-piece hood and full fleece lining, it&rsquo;s the perfect pullover for all-day easy wear. Complete with concealed zip pockets and woven logo tab.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>100% Polyester.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model is 6&#39;4&quot; and wears size L.</p>', 0, 0, '2018-07-26 04:12:35', '2018-11-28 03:57:03'),
