(87, 'Fashion 3-Station Integrated Training Machine', 'fashion-3station-integrated-training-machine', 9, 1, 160, 34, 150, 'null', 'hort9-61534042529.jpg', '[]', 'Assemble Space:（L*W*H）: 2300*1850*2065（mm）', '<p>Function: leg press, leg extension, chest extension, high pull, low pull, and abdomen-press etc.<br />\r\n 2300*1850*2065（mm）<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFunction Features<br />\r\nInnovative design, compact structure, can be used by five people simultaneously.<br />\r\nTotal Two towers，40pcs <strong>cast iron  </strong>Weight stacks ，20 pieces per tower for household trainer, 10pounds/pc</p>', 3, 0, '2018-08-12 02:55:29', '2018-11-28 03:57:03'),
(88, 'Bio-Arc Series', 'bioarc-series', 0, 1, 300, 10, 300, '', 'e8-31534042893.jpg', '[\"e8-21534042893.jpg\",\"e8-21534042893.jpg\"]', 'TuﬀStuﬀ is proud to introduce the Bio-Arc strength series, the ﬁrst resistance machines to incorporate multiplanar movement of each machine’s seat, along a linear arc trajectory', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>R&amp;D</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>TuﬀStuﬀ is proud to introduce the Bio-Arc strength series, the ﬁrst resistance machines to incorporate multiplanar movement of each machine&rsquo;s seat, along a linear arc trajectory. The seat movement allows the user to move along the arc path in conjunction with the machine helping to maintain more optimal muscle length and improving the force of contraction and training stimulus. Three years in the making, from concepts and engineering to prototype, testing and reﬁnements. Each of the Bio-Arc line&#39;s machines were tested, following initial design positioning, by an independent exercise consulting company. Pilot research studies combining joint positioning &ndash; using goniometry testing, along with muscle recruitment<strong>and activity measurements &ndash; through electromyographic (EMG) testing were performed to determine the optimal dimensions of each unit for ﬁnal production. Every detail and design modiﬁcations were executed to exact speciﬁcations and re-tested. The end results, a patented&nbsp;</strong><strong>Bio-Arc Technology that allows full body linear arc trajectory motion during execution of</strong><br />\r\n<strong>the exercise!</strong></p>', 0, 0, '2018-08-12 03:01:33', '2018-11-19 15:04:09'),
